revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Floor_RaiseByValueTxTy}} {{Special|239|tag, speed, height|Floor|RaiseByValueTxTy}}
* ''tag'': Tag of affected sector * ''speed'': How quickly the floor moves * ''height'': Amount to raise floor by
Raises a tagged sector's floor by height units and uses the trigger change model to give it a new picture and special. If ''tag'' is 0, then the sector on the line's back side is used.
== Examples ==
{{noexamples}}
